Question 5

Repeat Question 4 using the Tidymodels syntax.

baseball_recipe = recipe(Wpct ~ RD, data = baseball) %>% step_dummy(all_nominal())

lm_workflow = workflow() %>% add_model(lm_model) %>% add_recipe(baseball_recipe)

lm_fit = fit(lm_workflow, baseball)
